{"word":"ἐπάνω","slug":"ἐπάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπάνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἄνω</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>above, atop, on the upper side</i> or <i>part</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <el>ὁ ἐπάνω πύργος</el> the <i>upper</i> tower, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>above</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>above</i>, in a book, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>supra</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>of Number, <i>above, more than</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}